description:
Let you easy to use different fonts for Latin and CJK characters in selected text layers.

您可以在选中的文本图层上轻松为中西文应用不同字体。

You can import rules from JSON file, also can export them for sharing.

您可以从 JSON 文件导入规则，亦可将其导出用于共享。

```
[
  {
    "group": "Android",
    "fonts": [
      {"family":"Roboto","style":"Light"},
      {"family":"Noto Sans CJK SC","style":"Light"}
    ]
  },
  {
    "group": "Android",
    "fonts": [
      {"family":"Roboto","style":"Regular"},
      {"family":"Noto Sans CJK SC","style":"Regular"}
    ]
  }
]
```

The first item in fonts array in JSON is font for Latin characters, and the second item for CJK characters.

JSON 中的 fonts 数组第一项为西文字体，第二项为中日韩字体。
